reviewText: This was the oldest Whitetail Madness video in DVD which I did not have.  To see an old buck such as Skyscaper, was exciting!  You just don't see many bucks this old with a large rack on his head.  And with drop tines as a bonus!  I love it when Mark Drury shared this buck with his friends and family!  What a video!
Bought for my husband - he had to have this one! And he loves it. It's the Drury guys - who wouldn't!
